snippet: A day after President Obama told an Ohio radio station that he was not a fan of Tim Tebow’s being on the Jets, Coach Rex Ryan resisted taking a humorous swipe back.
abstract: NFL Roundup; New York Jets coach Rex Ryan resists taking a humorous swipe after Pres Obama weighs in on the potential for quarterback controversy between Jets starter Mark Sanchez and backup Tim Tebow; other NFL news noted.
lead_paragraph: A day after President Obama told an Ohio radio station that he was not a fan of Tim Tebow’s being on the Jets, Coach Rex Ryan resisted taking a humorous swipe back.

headline.seo: Rex Ryan Lays Off Obama for Opinion on Tim Tebow
